### ğŸ“œ `users` Table  
| Column Name | Type | Description |
|-------------|------|-------------|
| user_id     | integer | Unique user ID (PK) |
| city        | string  | User's city |
| email       | string  | User's email |
| signup_date | datetime | User's sign-up date |

#### ğŸ“ Example Input:
