## ğŸ¯ **Expected Output**
| order_id | user_id | quantity | status | date | price | user_id | city | email | signup_date |
|----------|--------|----------|----------|---------------------|------|--------|-------------|---------------------|
| 100102   | 111    | 10       | Completed  | 08/17/2022 12:00:00 | 10.00 | 111 | San Francisco | rrok10@gmail.com | 08/03/2021 12:00:00 |
