## ğŸ§ **Explanation:**  
Each trade in `trades` is **joined** with user details from `users` using `user_id`.  

ğŸš€ **The dataset may have different inputs & outputs â€“ this is just an example!**  


SQL QUERY:
SELECT * FROM 
trades as t JOIN users as u 
on t.user_id = u.user_id;
